<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF109-580-005  </DOCNO><DOCID>09 580 005.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>LAN Magazine  Nov 1990 v5 n11 p178(2)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Telecon Library Inc. 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Expanded Isolan. (BICC Data Network's Isolan EtherConnect System/4wiring hub) (product announcement)andM;</TITLE><DESCRIPT>Company:   BICC Data Networks Inc. (Product introduction).andO;Product:   BICC Data Networks ISOLAN EtherConnect System/4 Structured WiringHub (Network hub) (Product introduction).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionNetwork HubsEthernetCommunications Boards-Cards.andO;Feature:   illustrationphotograph.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Expanded IsolanandM;BICC Data Networks's new Isolan EtherConnect System/4 (ECS/4) wiring hub isdesigned for the small office.andP;  This Ethernet wiring chassis can accommodateup to four plug-in cards such as multimedia repeaters, bridges, and multiporttransceivers.andP;  Local and remote management are supported.andM;The ECS/4 uses a distributed repeater architecture, which prevents a failureof one repeater card from affecting the entire network.andP;  Each card containsits own built-in repeater chip.andP;  Only segments attached to the failedrepeater card would be impacted by a repeater failure.andM;Also announced are two products that support Shielded Twisted Pair (STP): the1201-3 STP System and the 1182 STP Transceiver.andP;  Isolan also supportsshielded twisted-pair, thick and thin coax, and fiber-optic cabling.andP;  The STPsystem, including an STP repeater card, distribution panel, and connectingcable, allows users to operate on an Ethernet implemented on the IBM CablingSystem in a building wired with STP.andM;A bridge card is also new.andP;  The 1205 Managed Bridge Line Card allows Ethernetto be bridged.andP;  Highspeed filtering and forwarding rates and duplicate pathoperation are made possible by the spanning tree algorithm.andP;  BICC's IsoviewNetwork Manager can monitor, confligure, and control the bridge cardremotely.andM;The EtherConnect System/4 costs $1,595; line cards and management card aresold separately.andP;  The 1201-3 STP System costs $1,595 for a repeater linecard, distribution panel, and connecting cable.andP;  The 1203-1 STP RLC alone is$1,295.andP;  The 1182 STP Transceiver is priced at $195.andP;  The 1205 Managed BridgeLine Card is priced at $4,495.andM;BICC Data Networks, 1800 West Park Dr., Westboro, Mass.andP;  01581, (508)898-2422.andO;</TEXT></DOC>